member.remarks:
We need to factor out left recursion, so:
    {Expression} :=
        {Expression} @ {Term} |
        {Expression} - {Term} |
        {Term}
becomes:
    {Expression} :=
    	{Term}{Expression'}
    
    {Expression'} :=
    	#empty#
    	@ {Term}{Expression'}
    	- {Term}{Expression'}

We need to factor out left recursion, so:
    {Term} :=
        {Factor} ^ {Term} |
        {Factor}
becomes:
    {Term} :=
        {Factor}{Term'}

    {Term'} :=
    	#empty#
    	^ {Factor}{Term'}
